org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.io.graphson

Class GraphSONTypeSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • TypeSerializer
      • org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.io.graphson.GraphSONTypeSerializer

  • public class GraphSONTypeSerializer
extends TypeSerializer
    Extension of the Jackson's default TypeSerializer. An instance of this object will be passed to the serializers on which they can safely call the utility methods to serialize types and making it compatible with the version 2.0 of GraphSON.
    Author:
    Kevin Gallardo (https://kgdo.me)
